56 /* glcorearb.h is for use with OpenGL core profile implementations.
57 ** It should should be placed in the same directory as gl.h and
58 ** included as <GL/glcorearb.h>.
59 **
60 ** glcorearb.h includes only APIs in the latest OpenGL core profile
61 ** implementation together with APIs in newer ARB extensions which
62 ** can be supported by the core profile. It does not, and never will
63 ** include functionality removed from the core profile, such as
64 ** fixed-function vertex and fragment processing.
65 **
66 ** Do not #include both <GL/glcorearb.h> and either of <GL/gl.h> or
67 ** <GL/glext.h> in the same source file.
68 */
69

1499 #ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1500 /* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
1501 #define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1502 /* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
1503 /* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
1504 #if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
1505 #include <inttypes.h>
1506 #elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
1507 #include <inttypes.h>
1508 #if defined(__STDC__)
1509 #if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
1510 typedef long int int64_t;
1511 typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
1512 #else
1513 typedef long long int int64_t;
1514 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1515 #endif /* __arch64__ */
1516 #endif /* __STDC__ */
1517 #elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
1518 #include <inttypes.h>
1519 #elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
1520 #include <stdint.h>
1521 #elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
1522 typedef long int int32_t;
1523 typedef long long int int64_t;
1524 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1525 #elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
1526 #include <stdint.h>
1527 #elif defined(_WIN32)
1528 typedef __int32 int32_t;
1529 typedef __int64 int64_t;
1530 typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
1531 #else
1532 /* Fallback if nothing above works */
1533 #include <inttypes.h>
1534 #endif
1535 #endif
